  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.5.4-stable\r\nOS & Version: Windows 10\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nWhen I create two nodes **on two different hosts**, i can send ethers from one node to the other.\r\nNow when I create two nodes **on the same host**, i expect to be able to send ether from noe node to the other.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nWhen the two nodes are hosted on the same machine, i fail to send ethers from one to the other.\r\n\r\nQuestions:\r\n1. is this an exptected behaviour?\r\n2. if yes, why?",
